videoDetails.Title: Ground Battles are nothing more but Air Battles now  War Thunder
videoDetails.Description:
So after a very long time I dropped some WT realistic ground battles, decided to hop into my fav 6.0 BR with panthers and tigers and p.....planes....a bunch of mothertrucking planes. There's more planes than tanks...  

Imagine if GROUND battles were actually ground vehicles against ground vehicles....I know right.  

At least it gave me a chance to show my AA skills.  

Enjoy and have fun watching ;)
